# COMMON OS ADOPTION REVIEW WORKFLOW CANONICAL

status: canonical
layer: development

## Adoption review steps
1. Identify target surface
2. Check fit against CommonOS scope
3. Confirm that domain truth remains domain-owned
4. Confirm that secrets and authority stay server-side
5. Approve shared adoption or reject with reason

## Review focus
- reuse value
- boundary correctness
- implementation practicality
- ERP applicability where relevant



