# COMMON OS CHANGE INTRODUCTION POLICY CANONICAL

status: canonical
layer: development

## Policy
- prefer additive introduction
- prefer variant extension before branching
- preserve compatibility where practical
- document migration when naming changes
- keep CommonOS names canonical for new assets

## Rule
Legacy references may remain as historical sources, but new canonical assets must use CommonOS terminology.



